Title: A Note on Conifolds

Authors: Kiyoshi Higashijima, Tetsuji Kimura and Muneto Nitta (Osaka Univ.)

Comments: LaTeX2e, 8 pages, no figures, accepted for publication in Physics

Letters BJournal-ref: Phys.Lett. B518 (2001) 301-305

We present the Ricci-flat metric and its Kahler potential on the conifoldwith the O(N) isometry, whose conical singularity is repaired by the complexquadric surface Q^{N-2} = SO(N)/SO(N-2)xU(1).